<section id="impact">
  <h2>Global Impact</h2>
  <h3>GreenGrade App</h3>

  <div class="image-row">
    <img src="greengrade-input.png" class="app-image">
    <img src="greengrade-sample.png" class="app-image">
  </div>

  <p>
    SII is implemented in the <strong>Sustainability Interval Index App</strong> app, which evaluates corporate sustainability
    using either manual inputs or automatically extracted data from annual reports.
  </p>
  <p>
    Beyond scoring, <strong>Sustainability Interval Index App</strong> delivers actionable feedback by identifying which sustainability
    indicators most constrain a company’s rating. This transforms sustainability analysis from a
    static judgment into a practical roadmap for measurable improvement.
  </p>
</section>

